1
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:33,000
"Bittersweet Love"

2
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:38,200
(1992 Yunjing)

3
00:01:38,256 --> 00:01:39,881
Lu Xiaofan once believed

4
00:01:40,381 --> 00:01:42,631
he could stand shoulder
to shoulder with him.

5
00:01:43,881 --> 00:01:45,631
But reality told him

6
00:01:45,965 --> 00:01:47,131
it was a pipe dream.

7
00:01:48,423 --> 00:01:50,965
Some people are born on top,

8
00:01:51,131 --> 00:01:54,215
while he, Lu Xiaofan, is at the bottom.

9
00:01:55,423 --> 00:01:56,631
Those at the bottom

10
00:01:56,798 --> 00:01:59,715
have to live and want accordingly.

11
00:02:00,715 --> 00:02:01,465
Otherwise...

12
00:02:01,631 --> 00:02:02,631
Bro.

13
00:02:02,715 --> 00:02:03,798
Long time no see.

14
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:05,340
Have you eaten yet?

15
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:07,590
Not yet.

16
00:02:09,173 --> 00:02:09,798
How about

17
00:02:09,965 --> 00:02:11,090
I take you out to eat?

18
00:02:11,256 --> 00:02:12,256
No need.

19
00:02:23,215 --> 00:02:25,048
So what brings you here?

20
00:02:26,631 --> 00:02:28,590
Is your family asking for money again?

21
00:02:29,340 --> 00:02:31,340
Or is your brother
unhappy with his job again?

22
00:02:32,215 --> 00:02:33,756
Or something else?

23
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:39,298
My mom wants to visit me in Yunjing.

24
00:02:39,548 --> 00:02:41,881
Didn't you head back recently?

25
00:02:42,631 --> 00:02:43,881
If Mrs. Lu misses you,

26
00:02:44,590 --> 00:02:45,881
just go back for another visit.

27
00:02:49,173 --> 00:02:51,590
She also wants to look around in Yunjing.

28
00:02:54,465 --> 00:02:55,465
When they get here,

29
00:02:55,506 --> 00:02:56,546
can't you look after them?

30
00:02:58,715 --> 00:03:01,423
She also wants to see Lüxin.

31
00:03:04,090 --> 00:03:05,090
How about

32
00:03:05,965 --> 00:03:07,381
giving her a call?

33
00:03:15,590 --> 00:03:16,215
Alright.

34
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:17,590
I got it.

35
00:03:22,215 --> 00:03:23,215
Bro.

36
00:03:23,715 --> 00:03:25,090
You really won't eat?

37
00:03:27,798 --> 00:03:28,798
I'm not hungry.

38
00:03:31,298 --> 00:03:32,298
Well,

39
00:03:34,381 --> 00:03:35,381
I'm leaving.

40
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:09,000
(Episode 1)

41
00:04:09,024 --> 00:04:11,024
(1990 Yunxi)

42
00:04:13,006 --> 00:04:14,006
Fanfan.

43
00:04:14,256 --> 00:04:16,423
From now on, you're an adult.

44
00:04:17,548 --> 00:04:18,548
You have to understand,

45
00:04:18,549 --> 00:04:21,090
nothing in life is all good,

46
00:04:21,465 --> 00:04:23,798
nor all bad.

47
00:04:25,256 --> 00:04:27,548
The Bei family. Big
officials in the capital.

48
00:04:28,173 --> 00:04:31,298
What's up? Marrying into money?

49
00:04:33,298 --> 00:04:35,965
Lu Xiaoping is the eldest
son of the Lu family.

50
00:04:36,256 --> 00:04:38,840
Having him marry into their family

51
00:04:39,090 --> 00:04:40,548
goes against both reason and custom.

52
00:04:41,173 --> 00:04:42,173
Alright then.

53
00:04:42,465 --> 00:04:43,465
In my eyes,

54
00:04:43,506 --> 00:04:45,756
Xiaofan is a very well-behaved boy.

55
00:04:46,173 --> 00:04:48,006
Fanfan, come on, call him Dad.

56
00:05:05,881 --> 00:05:07,131
Who is it?

57
00:05:08,631 --> 00:05:09,631
I

58
00:05:09,965 --> 00:05:11,365
I didn't know you were in the room.

59
00:05:11,965 --> 00:05:14,172
Don't think marrying me means
a hick like you gets my bed.

60
00:05:14,173 --> 00:05:15,381
That's not what I meant.

61
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,340
I'll make do on the sofa tonight.

62
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:19,340
Get out.

63
00:05:33,340 --> 00:05:33,881
This time,

64
00:05:34,090 --> 00:05:35,610
the Bei family must give us an answer.

65
00:05:36,298 --> 00:05:37,256
Keep your voice down.

66
00:05:37,257 --> 00:05:38,524
You want everyone to hear you, huh?

67
00:05:38,548 --> 00:05:39,548
The deed's already done.

68
00:05:39,631 --> 00:05:40,631
So what?

69
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:41,840
Call it off.

70
00:05:41,881 --> 00:05:43,340
His daughter has a shady past.

71
00:05:43,590 --> 00:05:45,423
She's carrying an illegitimate child.

72
00:05:46,131 --> 00:05:47,756
The Beis are officials in the capital

73
00:05:48,048 --> 00:05:49,131
and fear a scandal.

74
00:05:49,756 --> 00:05:50,965
Does that mean

75
00:05:51,465 --> 00:05:52,840
they can prey on the Lu family?

76
00:05:53,715 --> 00:05:54,715
I knew it,

77
00:05:55,090 --> 00:05:56,210
no wonder he's back in town,

78
00:05:56,465 --> 00:05:58,340
still clinging to this childhood betrothal.

79
00:05:58,881 --> 00:05:59,423
The door isn't closed yet.

80
00:05:59,423 --> 00:06:00,423
Go on, close it! Hurry!

81
00:06:05,298 --> 00:06:06,755
You want the whole village to find out

82
00:06:06,756 --> 00:06:07,839
your daughter-in-law got knocked up

83
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,360
before she even crossed the threshold?

84
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:12,029
And left your son
a cuckold?

85
00:06:12,798 --> 00:06:14,038
If this marriage is called off,

86
00:06:14,173 --> 00:06:15,548
he'll lose all his face too.

87
00:06:16,090 --> 00:06:16,548
Lu Zhenxing,

88
00:06:16,923 --> 00:06:19,090
Don't think
I am as petty as you,

89
00:06:19,381 --> 00:06:21,482
just drooling over that
two-thousand-yuan bride price.

90
00:06:21,506 --> 00:06:23,048
Xiaofan has been wronged a little,

91
00:06:23,798 --> 00:06:24,839
but it's still better than

92
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:26,381
rotting in the countryside farming.

93
00:06:27,423 --> 00:06:28,756
Pingping is set to graduate.

94
00:06:29,048 --> 00:06:30,232
With the Bei family backing him,

95
00:06:30,256 --> 00:06:31,423
he can get

96
00:06:31,715 --> 00:06:32,840
an official post in Yunjing.

97
00:06:34,465 --> 00:06:35,465
And the youngest one,

98
00:06:35,798 --> 00:06:36,673
when she grows up,

99
00:06:36,715 --> 00:06:37,923
she can study in city colleges

100
00:06:38,131 --> 00:06:39,298
and become a city dweller.

101
00:06:41,465 --> 00:06:42,048
Alright.

102
00:06:42,215 --> 00:06:43,215
Stop moping.

103
00:06:43,590 --> 00:06:44,941
The villagers will come
asking for red envelopes soon.

104
00:06:44,965 --> 00:06:45,965
Let's go.

105
00:06:56,923 --> 00:06:57,465
Hey, listen,

106
00:06:57,466 --> 00:06:58,798
Why not hit the newlyweds’ room?

107
00:07:00,340 --> 00:07:01,756
Anybody's fine for red envelopes,

108
00:07:02,215 --> 00:07:03,840
the Lus won't shell out much.

109
00:07:04,256 --> 00:07:05,090
Yo!

110
00:07:05,173 --> 00:07:06,465
Isn't this the groom?

111
00:07:07,090 --> 00:07:08,090
Yeah.

112
00:07:08,131 --> 00:07:09,232
Looks like he's had too much.

113
00:07:09,256 --> 00:07:10,590
Doesn't the bride care?

114
00:07:10,881 --> 00:07:12,255
Bet the bride

115
00:07:12,256 --> 00:07:13,256
chased him out, huh?

116
00:07:13,423 --> 00:07:14,964
Marrying up is no picnic.

117
00:07:14,965 --> 00:07:15,965
Hey!

118
00:07:16,131 --> 00:07:17,465
They're already married,

119
00:07:17,756 --> 00:07:19,881
and you're still gossiping
behind their backs.

120
00:07:20,215 --> 00:07:21,255
Come on, help him up.

121
00:07:21,256 --> 00:07:22,215
Help him up.

122
00:07:22,215 --> 00:07:23,215
Come on, groom.

123
00:07:25,548 --> 00:07:26,672
Alright, let's take him back.

124
00:07:26,673 --> 00:07:28,107
The bride didn't even
come out to toast today.

125
00:07:28,131 --> 00:07:28,881
I didn't even get a good look.

126
00:07:29,090 --> 00:07:30,090
Let's go.

127
00:07:30,506 --> 00:07:31,965
Don't I know you?

128
00:07:32,715 --> 00:07:34,172
Just thinking about that sleazy stuff.

129
00:07:34,173 --> 00:07:34,923
Oh, please.

130
00:07:34,923 --> 00:07:35,798
Like you don't want to see?

131
00:07:35,798 --> 00:07:36,798
Then don't go.

132
00:08:01,548 --> 00:08:02,548
Mr. Bei.

133
00:08:07,090 --> 00:08:08,673
Who's this guy, so full of himself?

134
00:08:08,798 --> 00:08:10,465
Eldest Young Master Bei, Bei Lüqing.

135
00:08:12,048 --> 00:08:13,506
Lu Xiaofan never thought

136
00:08:14,173 --> 00:08:16,173
that trapped in such dire circumstances,

137
00:08:17,048 --> 00:08:19,506
his only saving grace was.

138
00:08:20,298 --> 00:08:21,673
Bei Lüxin's older brother.

139
00:08:23,131 --> 00:08:24,840
At that moment, he couldn't foresee

140
00:08:25,340 --> 00:08:26,715
that in the days to come,

141
00:08:27,048 --> 00:08:28,756
this unexpected closeness

142
00:08:28,881 --> 00:08:30,923
would change his entire life.

143
00:08:42,798 --> 00:08:43,798
Alright.

144
00:08:43,923 --> 00:08:44,923
Drop the act.

145
00:08:57,423 --> 00:08:58,423
Bro,

146
00:08:58,923 --> 00:09:00,131
you caught me.

147
00:09:01,090 --> 00:09:02,173
Where were you going?

148
00:09:06,256 --> 00:09:07,340
Stay here tonight.

149
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:37,340
Go take a shower.

150
00:10:49,465 --> 00:10:51,465
Bro, I—I'm done.

151
00:10:54,465 --> 00:10:55,465
Done?

152
00:11:04,048 --> 00:11:05,506
Did you forget to wash your hair?

153
00:11:06,756 --> 00:11:08,506
No, no need.

154
00:11:09,006 --> 00:11:10,465
It'd be a waste of water.

155
00:11:14,506 --> 00:11:15,756
About showering,

156
00:11:15,923 --> 00:11:17,256
Lu Xiaofan really had no clue.

157
00:11:18,381 --> 00:11:20,380
Besides, last night, for the wedding,

158
00:11:20,381 --> 00:11:21,840
he had just washed.

159
00:11:22,631 --> 00:11:24,256
Not until Bei Lüqing went in with him

160
00:11:24,798 --> 00:11:26,006
did Lu Xiaofan realize

161
00:11:26,965 --> 00:11:28,714
that taking a shower in the city

162
00:11:28,715 --> 00:11:30,423
meant washing from head to toe,

163
00:11:30,798 --> 00:11:33,423
not just a pair of feet.

164
00:12:24,756 --> 00:12:25,965
The left one's for hair,

165
00:12:26,465 --> 00:12:27,881
The right one's for body.

166
00:12:29,298 --> 00:12:30,465
Wash yourself properly.

167
00:12:48,381 --> 00:12:50,047
Don't think marrying me means

168
00:12:50,048 --> 00:12:51,340
a hick like you gets my bed.

169
00:12:52,381 --> 00:12:53,381
Get out.

170
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,840
Bro.

171
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:20,340
What's wrong?

172
00:13:20,881 --> 00:13:22,256
My clothes are all wet.

173
00:13:22,590 --> 00:13:23,840
Just wear mine tomorrow.

174
00:13:26,631 --> 00:13:27,631
They're all

175
00:13:28,006 --> 00:13:29,131
all wet.

176
00:14:55,715 --> 00:14:56,715
Bro.

177
00:14:56,965 --> 00:14:58,881
Can I borrow your cassette player?

178
00:15:00,923 --> 00:15:01,923
Mm.

179
00:15:03,381 --> 00:15:04,923
At the wedding,

180
00:15:05,215 --> 00:15:06,505
my little sister said she wanted to...

181
00:15:06,506 --> 00:15:08,090
I don't have a cassette player.

182
00:15:11,090 --> 00:15:12,090
This one here?

183
00:15:12,798 --> 00:15:14,006
It's a CD player.

184
00:15:14,631 --> 00:15:16,256
A CD player?

185
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:17,923
Got it in Japan.

186
00:15:18,256 --> 00:15:19,896
It's totally normal you haven't seen one.

187
00:15:20,673 --> 00:15:21,673
No.

188
00:15:23,131 --> 00:15:24,131
Never mind.

189
00:15:24,673 --> 00:15:25,673
Never mind.

190
00:15:26,381 --> 00:15:27,981
Give it to your sister tomorrow morning.

191
00:15:28,048 --> 00:15:29,568
We're not leaving until the afternoon.

192
00:15:56,965 --> 00:15:57,965
Smells off.

193
00:16:04,590 --> 00:16:05,923
You swapped them.

194
00:16:16,548 --> 00:16:17,548
I mean,

195
00:16:18,340 --> 00:16:20,673
you mixed up shampoo and body wash.

196
00:17:10,631 --> 00:17:12,715
Xiaofan's perfect in all respects,

197
00:17:12,965 --> 00:17:14,839
just a quiet kid.

198
00:17:14,840 --> 00:17:15,881
From now on,

199
00:17:16,048 --> 00:17:18,256
please keep an eye on him.

200
00:17:18,798 --> 00:17:19,631
It's no trouble at all.

201
00:17:19,632 --> 00:17:22,215
He's steady and well-behaved.

202
00:17:22,756 --> 00:17:23,298
Xiaofan.

203
00:17:23,298 --> 00:17:24,298
Come here.

204
00:17:28,631 --> 00:17:29,631
Once you're over there,

205
00:17:29,706 --> 00:17:32,039
take after Uncle Bei and your brother-in-law.

206
00:17:32,548 --> 00:17:34,048
Don't worry, Mrs. Lu.

207
00:17:34,465 --> 00:17:36,506
Call us when you get there.

208
00:17:36,840 --> 00:17:38,215
Xiaofan isn't that dim-witted.

209
00:17:38,423 --> 00:17:39,755
He won't forget his brother.

210
00:17:39,756 --> 00:17:40,756
Right?

211
00:17:43,255 --> 00:17:44,255
Little one,

212
00:17:45,423 --> 00:17:46,798
where's Brother Bei's CD player?

213
00:17:47,215 --> 00:17:48,215
Mom.

214
00:17:48,256 --> 00:17:48,881
I

215
00:17:49,048 --> 00:17:50,881
I broke the CD player.

216
00:17:51,048 --> 00:17:52,214
How could you?

217
00:17:52,215 --> 00:17:54,423
How could you break Brother Bei's things?

218
00:17:54,673 --> 00:17:55,798
Give me the player, quick.

219
00:17:55,881 --> 00:17:57,321
I'll head into town to get it fixed.

220
00:17:57,673 --> 00:17:59,089
Hurry up and get it out!

221
00:17:59,090 --> 00:18:00,256
It's gone.

222
00:18:01,423 --> 00:18:02,340
It's gone?

223
00:18:02,341 --> 00:18:03,422
It was already broken.

224
00:18:03,423 --> 00:18:04,464
I wasn't paying attention,

225
00:18:04,465 --> 00:18:05,840
and someone must have taken it.

226
00:18:06,631 --> 00:18:08,881
How could you lose the player?!

227
00:18:09,965 --> 00:18:11,047
What's the big deal?

228
00:18:11,048 --> 00:18:11,756
I'll give you money.

229
00:18:11,756 --> 00:18:12,715
When you arrive in Yunjing,

230
00:18:12,716 --> 00:18:13,774
get Bei Lüqing another one.

231
00:18:13,798 --> 00:18:14,381
Mom.

232
00:18:14,506 --> 00:18:15,590
It's just a CD player.

233
00:18:16,131 --> 00:18:17,491
My brother married their daughter.

234
00:18:17,548 --> 00:18:18,756
Consider it a gift for me.

235
00:18:18,923 --> 00:18:19,982
It can't be worth much anyway.

236
00:18:20,006 --> 00:18:21,006
Watch your mouth.

237
00:18:24,215 --> 00:18:25,255
No matter how valuable
your Lu family son is,

238
00:18:25,256 --> 00:18:26,506
you can only sell him once.

239
00:18:27,173 --> 00:18:29,093
Didn't you just get two
thousand in bride price?

240
00:18:29,256 --> 00:18:31,048
My brother's player cost three thousand.

241
00:18:31,673 --> 00:18:33,506
It was a birthday gift from my mom.

242
00:18:33,874 --> 00:18:35,749
Offering to pay? He might not take it.

243
00:18:36,881 --> 00:18:37,881
Even if he does,

244
00:18:38,150 --> 00:18:39,941
your son won't cut it.

245
00:18:39,965 --> 00:18:41,245
You'd still owe a thousand more.

246
00:18:42,215 --> 00:18:43,255
You wretched child!

247
00:18:43,256 --> 00:18:43,631
Mom.

248
00:18:43,673 --> 00:18:45,131
Lüxin, watch your mouth!

249
00:18:45,298 --> 00:18:47,173
Is that any way to talk to your elders?

250
00:18:47,923 --> 00:18:48,298
Mom.

251
00:18:48,631 --> 00:18:49,215
Say no more!

252
00:18:49,506 --> 00:18:50,506
Alright, alright.

253
00:18:50,840 --> 00:18:51,465
Forget it, forget it.

254
00:18:51,631 --> 00:18:52,951
You're making a fool of yourself.

255
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:54,340
Come here.

256
00:18:55,798 --> 00:18:56,881
Father-in-law.

257
00:18:56,965 --> 00:18:58,173
Sorry you had to see that.

258
00:18:58,673 --> 00:19:00,393
But if you don't teach a daughter yourself,

259
00:19:00,590 --> 00:19:01,790
she'll grow up to be a menace.

260
00:19:02,298 --> 00:19:03,631
And if she has no shame,

261
00:19:03,881 --> 00:19:06,590
it reflects poorly on us
parents too, doesn't it?

262
00:19:08,256 --> 00:19:09,798
You're right.

263
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:13,423
As for the CD player...

264
00:19:15,090 --> 00:19:16,630
it's not really worth much.

265
00:19:16,631 --> 00:19:17,631
If it's lost, so be it.

266
00:19:19,506 --> 00:19:20,546
Go on, thank your Brother Bei.

267
00:19:21,798 --> 00:19:22,958
Xiaofan is my brother-in-law.

268
00:19:23,173 --> 00:19:24,173
We’re all family.

269
00:19:24,423 --> 00:19:25,423
That CD player,

270
00:19:25,923 --> 00:19:27,381
I only lent it to him,

271
00:19:27,715 --> 00:19:29,215
So naturally it's on him.

272
00:19:30,465 --> 00:19:31,465
Thank you, Brother Bei.

273
00:19:34,215 --> 00:19:35,797
Mrs. Lu made the wedding

274
00:19:35,798 --> 00:19:37,256
really grand this time.

275
00:19:37,756 --> 00:19:39,173
But Lu Xiaofan knew

276
00:19:39,465 --> 00:19:41,590
she didn't use up the entire bride price.

277
00:19:42,631 --> 00:19:43,965
Mrs. Lu greeted the guests.

278
00:19:44,131 --> 00:19:46,131
She also took the red envelopes.

279
00:19:47,048 --> 00:19:49,048
But the little one lost
Bei Lüqing’s CD player,

280
00:19:49,256 --> 00:19:50,696
yet she refused to shell out a cent.

281
00:19:51,923 --> 00:19:53,465
Whenever Lu Xiaofan thought of this,

282
00:19:53,881 --> 00:19:55,006
he felt utterly inferior.

283
00:19:56,381 --> 00:19:57,589
Thinking of Bei Lüqing,

284
00:19:57,590 --> 00:19:59,631
who must look down on their entire family,

285
00:20:00,173 --> 00:20:02,756
Lu Xiaofan felt even more inferior.

286
00:20:03,631 --> 00:20:04,631
Mom.

287
00:20:06,298 --> 00:20:07,298
Dad.

288
00:20:10,756 --> 00:20:11,965
I'll be off then.

289
00:20:12,756 --> 00:20:13,756
Take care.

290
00:20:14,006 --> 00:20:15,046
Look after yourself, okay?

291
00:20:15,090 --> 00:20:16,090
Mm.

292
00:21:04,298 --> 00:21:05,298
Wait.

293
00:21:06,548 --> 00:21:08,256
Wait, Xiaofan.

294
00:21:09,256 --> 00:21:11,298
Xiaofan, wait!

295
00:21:12,215 --> 00:21:13,423
Hold on.

296
00:21:14,131 --> 00:21:14,631
Stop the car.

297
00:21:14,756 --> 00:21:15,965
What are you doing?

298
00:21:20,798 --> 00:21:21,798
Fanfan.

299
00:21:22,381 --> 00:21:23,381
Mom.

300
00:21:23,506 --> 00:21:24,131
Mom.

301
00:21:24,131 --> 00:21:24,840
What's wrong?

302
00:21:24,840 --> 00:21:25,298
Here.

303
00:21:25,548 --> 00:21:27,256
Fanfan, quick, quick, put it away.

304
00:21:27,631 --> 00:21:28,631
Hide it well.

305
00:21:28,756 --> 00:21:30,381
If anything comes up once you arrive,

306
00:21:30,631 --> 00:21:31,173
call the township chief's house

307
00:21:31,174 --> 00:21:32,256
and give me a ring.

308
00:21:32,965 --> 00:21:34,685
If the Bei family dares to treat you badly,

309
00:21:35,131 --> 00:21:36,131
don't worry,

310
00:21:36,340 --> 00:21:37,340
I'll deal with them.

311
00:21:41,381 --> 00:21:42,298
Mom, you keep it.

312
00:21:42,299 --> 00:21:43,340
I can't take this.

313
00:21:43,506 --> 00:21:43,881
Quick.

314
00:21:44,340 --> 00:21:45,756
I can't, you keep it.

315
00:21:46,048 --> 00:21:47,048
Hurry, take it.

316
00:21:50,900 --> 00:21:51,608
Mrs. Lu.

317
00:21:51,632 --> 00:21:52,672
Don't worry.

318
00:21:52,673 --> 00:21:54,048
We'll take good care of Fanfan.

319
00:21:55,590 --> 00:21:56,590
Alright, alright.

320
00:21:57,465 --> 00:21:58,215
Go on back.

321
00:21:58,423 --> 00:21:59,423
Go on back.

322
00:22:00,756 --> 00:22:01,756
Ah.

323
00:22:24,131 --> 00:22:26,256
Can't bear to leave your
mom? Stay behind then.

324
00:22:34,965 --> 00:22:37,340
Lu Xiaofan, the second of four children,

325
00:22:37,881 --> 00:22:40,298
was always the one easily overlooked.

326
00:22:41,756 --> 00:22:43,214
He knew he paled in comparison

327
00:22:43,215 --> 00:22:44,923
to talkative Lu Xiaoping.

328
00:22:45,173 --> 00:22:46,673
So he never complained.

329
00:22:48,048 --> 00:22:49,548
But who hasn't dreamed

330
00:22:50,090 --> 00:22:51,048
that somewhere in this world

331
00:22:51,049 --> 00:22:52,840
there might be someone who favors them?

332
00:22:54,423 --> 00:22:55,715
Maybe there really is.

333
00:23:36,686 --> 00:23:39,820
[Yunhai Northwestern Airlines]

334
00:23:44,461 --> 00:23:46,755
(Yunjing, Bei Residence)

335
00:23:53,090 --> 00:23:55,756
Stepping into the Bei household,

336
00:23:56,131 --> 00:23:57,131
Lu Xiaofan felt like

337
00:23:57,381 --> 00:23:59,798
a country boy in the big city.

338
00:24:01,548 --> 00:24:02,506
It felt like a place

339
00:24:02,507 --> 00:24:04,173
to be revered,

340
00:24:04,631 --> 00:24:06,090
not a home.

341
00:24:11,756 --> 00:24:15,881
Perhaps he never truly
outgrew that feeling.

342
00:24:16,590 --> 00:24:17,590
Hey.

343
00:24:17,965 --> 00:24:18,965
Hello.

344
00:24:19,381 --> 00:24:21,506
You're Lu Xiaofan, aren't you?

345
00:24:22,548 --> 00:24:23,715
No need to be so nervous.

346
00:24:24,006 --> 00:24:26,298
I run the Bei household. I'm Lin.

347
00:24:26,631 --> 00:24:27,881
Just like Lüxin and the rest,

348
00:24:27,923 --> 00:24:28,965
call me Aunt Lin.

349
00:24:29,965 --> 00:24:31,005
Hello, Aunt Lin.

350
00:24:31,006 --> 00:24:31,423
Oh my, oh my.

351
00:24:31,423 --> 00:24:32,423
Alright, alright.

352
00:24:32,631 --> 00:24:33,465
There's no need for that.

353
00:24:33,506 --> 00:24:34,506
Come, follow me.

354
00:24:34,548 --> 00:24:35,548
Hey.

355
00:24:35,715 --> 00:24:36,381
It's not mealtime yet,

356
00:24:36,382 --> 00:24:38,715
but help yourself if you're hungry.

357
00:24:39,590 --> 00:24:40,673
Never used one before?

358
00:24:41,631 --> 00:24:42,797
Think of it like a root cellar.

359
00:24:42,798 --> 00:24:44,158
Make sure you shut the door tight.

360
00:24:44,340 --> 00:24:46,089
This is Mr. Bei's study.

361
00:24:46,090 --> 00:24:46,965
Don't enter unless needed,

362
00:24:46,966 --> 00:24:48,047
and knock first.

363
00:24:48,048 --> 00:24:49,048
Hey.

364
00:24:49,256 --> 00:24:50,880
Mr. Lüqing likes to have
academic discussions

365
00:24:50,881 --> 00:24:52,965
with his classmates in this little garden.

366
00:24:53,090 --> 00:24:54,399
Don't disturb them for no reason.

367
00:24:54,423 --> 00:24:57,048
Don't go into Lüxin and
Lüqing's rooms for no reason.

368
00:25:03,298 --> 00:25:04,673
This is your room.

369
00:25:06,090 --> 00:25:07,423
Don't mind the size.

370
00:25:07,465 --> 00:25:09,048
It's really bright inside.

371
00:25:09,840 --> 00:25:10,798
No, not at all.

372
00:25:10,840 --> 00:25:13,381
Bigger than my room at home.

373
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:17,090
Well, you rest up.

374
00:25:17,881 --> 00:25:18,881
Aunt Lin.

375
00:25:19,756 --> 00:25:20,756
Um.

376
00:25:21,090 --> 00:25:22,215
Lüxin, she...

377
00:25:22,715 --> 00:25:23,715
Xiaofan.

378
00:25:23,965 --> 00:25:24,965
The Bei family

379
00:25:25,048 --> 00:25:26,298
is no ordinary household.

380
00:25:26,548 --> 00:25:28,130
I don't know what your life

381
00:25:28,131 --> 00:25:29,340
was like before.

382
00:25:29,756 --> 00:25:30,798
Now that you're here,

383
00:25:31,090 --> 00:25:32,170
you have to learn to adapt.

384
00:25:32,548 --> 00:25:35,298
Don't ask questions
you shouldn't.

385
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:36,820
The Bei family will take care of you.

386
00:25:40,090 --> 00:25:41,340
Rest now, okay?

387
00:26:11,756 --> 00:26:12,756
Wait.

388
00:26:14,048 --> 00:26:15,381
Wait, Xiaofan.

389
00:26:16,548 --> 00:26:17,880
The Lu family must seize

390
00:26:17,881 --> 00:26:19,715
this golden opportunity.

391
00:26:21,090 --> 00:26:22,715
But Xiaofan couldn't help thinking.

392
00:26:23,881 --> 00:26:25,381
Lüxin was already pregnant.

393
00:26:25,548 --> 00:26:26,006
Here.

394
00:26:26,215 --> 00:26:27,215
Hide it well.

395
00:26:27,340 --> 00:26:29,060
If the Bei family dares to treat you badly,

396
00:26:29,298 --> 00:26:30,298
I'll deal with them.

397
00:26:30,840 --> 00:26:34,630
Why wouldn't his parents tell
him something like this directly?

398
00:26:38,590 --> 00:26:39,465
Lu Xiaofan,

399
00:26:39,466 --> 00:26:41,215
a mediocre and useless man,

400
00:26:42,006 --> 00:26:44,298
marrying a city girl,

401
00:26:44,631 --> 00:26:46,631
having a high-ranking
official as a father-in-law,

402
00:26:46,715 --> 00:26:48,756
and a big boss as a mother-in-law.

403
00:26:49,881 --> 00:26:50,756
All of this is the best repayment.

404
00:26:50,757 --> 00:26:52,923
Xiaofan can give his parents.

405
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:55,590
But

406
00:26:55,881 --> 00:26:57,340
within the Bei household,

407
00:26:57,673 --> 00:27:00,215
where exactly does Xiaofan stand?

408
00:27:06,673 --> 00:27:06,881
Hey.

409
00:27:06,965 --> 00:27:07,965
Hold on.

410
00:27:08,173 --> 00:27:09,673
Place a mat under hot dishes.

411
00:27:09,756 --> 00:27:11,256
It's a rosewood table.

412
00:27:19,298 --> 00:27:20,173
Xiaofan got up early

413
00:27:20,173 --> 00:27:20,965
with nothing to do,

414
00:27:21,131 --> 00:27:22,771
and insisted on learning to cook from me.

415
00:27:26,048 --> 00:27:27,048
Bro.

416
00:27:28,215 --> 00:27:29,298
Lüxin, she...

417
00:27:32,006 --> 00:27:33,006
Lu Xiaofan.

418
00:27:33,423 --> 00:27:34,482
You've shot to the top overnight,

419
00:27:34,506 --> 00:27:36,215
so why still act like a hick?

420
00:27:42,423 --> 00:27:43,423
Xiaofan.

421
00:27:44,173 --> 00:27:45,693
Don't bother with anything else today.

422
00:27:46,173 --> 00:27:47,373
Dad has something to tell you.

423
00:27:53,090 --> 00:27:54,090
Xiaofan,

424
00:27:55,423 --> 00:27:57,131
any ideas of your own?

425
00:28:01,465 --> 00:28:02,465
I

426
00:28:03,006 --> 00:28:04,715
I'm fine with any task.

427
00:28:05,298 --> 00:28:06,506
I just don't want to be idle.

428
00:28:08,590 --> 00:28:09,381
What I mean is,

429
00:28:09,590 --> 00:28:11,881
pick up your studies tomorrow.

430
00:28:12,173 --> 00:28:13,693
First, take the college entrance exam.

431
00:28:14,798 --> 00:28:15,131
No.

432
00:28:15,381 --> 00:28:16,541
No need for all that trouble.

433
00:28:17,715 --> 00:28:19,715
Studying takes time.

434
00:28:20,423 --> 00:28:22,006
I can do any kind of work.

435
00:28:22,256 --> 00:28:24,006
Back home I could carry bags of wheat

436
00:28:24,131 --> 00:28:26,256
and make several trips to town.

437
00:28:27,715 --> 00:28:28,756
It's fine.

438
00:28:29,298 --> 00:28:30,798
Since I made a promise to Mrs. Lu,

439
00:28:30,965 --> 00:28:31,965
I'll see it through.

440
00:28:32,048 --> 00:28:33,048
A few years of study

441
00:28:33,090 --> 00:28:34,090
is nothing to fear.

442
00:28:34,506 --> 00:28:35,506
Uncle Bei,

443
00:28:36,048 --> 00:28:37,381
really, don't go to any trouble.

444
00:28:39,090 --> 00:28:40,548
I didn't even finish middle school.

445
00:28:40,673 --> 00:28:41,756
There's no way I'll pass.

446
00:28:44,798 --> 00:28:46,238
You are the Bei family's son-in-law.

447
00:28:47,256 --> 00:28:48,336
The Beis need to save face,

448
00:28:48,965 --> 00:28:50,465
so you must act accordingly.

449
00:28:51,340 --> 00:28:52,340
Understood?

450
00:28:54,756 --> 00:28:56,548
Just hire a home tutor then.

451
00:28:59,715 --> 00:29:00,715
How about I teach him?

452
00:29:07,173 --> 00:29:08,173
Xiaofan,

453
00:29:08,340 --> 00:29:09,506
just learn from Lüqing.

454
00:29:09,840 --> 00:29:10,965
Don't feel pressured.

455
00:29:11,298 --> 00:29:12,506
Just make the cutoff score.

456
00:29:15,498 --> 00:29:17,258
["Family Feast: Cooking Recipies"]

457
00:29:22,465 --> 00:29:23,465
Bro.

458
00:29:30,256 --> 00:29:31,256
Try it on.

459
00:29:41,340 --> 00:29:41,756
Bro.

460
00:29:42,006 --> 00:29:42,548
No need.

461
00:29:42,673 --> 00:29:43,840
I brought plenty of clothes.

462
00:29:44,381 --> 00:29:45,381
Try it on.

463
00:29:46,631 --> 00:29:48,090
If it doesn't fit, I'll exchange it.

464
00:30:38,048 --> 00:30:39,048
Get up.

465
00:30:45,715 --> 00:30:46,715
Turn around.

466
00:30:52,256 --> 00:30:53,256
Bro.

467
00:30:53,381 --> 00:30:54,673
It's a perfect fit.

468
00:30:55,215 --> 00:30:56,465
You're amazing.

469
00:30:58,715 --> 00:31:00,006
Try on some pants too.

470
00:31:01,048 --> 00:31:02,048
Mm.

471
00:31:04,673 --> 00:31:05,798
Back in the Lu household,

472
00:31:06,548 --> 00:31:09,006
Xiaofan wore nothing but
his brother's hand-me-downs.

473
00:31:10,006 --> 00:31:11,673
Facing Bei Lüqing's kindness,

474
00:31:11,881 --> 00:31:13,340
Xiaofan couldn't help but wonder

475
00:31:14,090 --> 00:31:16,256
what could he possibly give in return?

476
00:32:01,590 --> 00:32:02,590
Bro.

477
00:32:03,423 --> 00:32:04,631
The pants

478
00:32:04,881 --> 00:32:06,381
are a bit tight.

479
00:32:09,381 --> 00:32:10,465
You'll get used to them.

480
00:32:34,256 --> 00:32:35,256
Get some sleep.

481
00:32:35,465 --> 00:32:36,785
I'll start teaching you tomorrow.

482
00:32:48,423 --> 00:32:49,423
Bro.

483
00:32:50,256 --> 00:32:51,465
Maybe let's just forget it.

484
00:32:56,048 --> 00:32:57,340
You'd better go for arts.

485
00:32:57,652 --> 00:33:00,366
For physics, chemistry and biology,
starting all over is really tough.

486
00:33:01,215 --> 00:33:01,798
Bro.

487
00:33:02,090 --> 00:33:03,756
Aren't you a science major?

488
00:33:04,131 --> 00:33:06,590
I can totally teach you arts as well.

489
00:33:13,756 --> 00:33:14,796
This CD player is for you.

490
00:33:16,256 --> 00:33:17,296
Your English is not great.

491
00:33:17,423 --> 00:33:18,423
You'll need it later.

492
00:33:19,256 --> 00:33:20,256
No, Bro, it's okay.

493
00:33:20,715 --> 00:33:21,756
It's too expensive.

494
00:33:22,298 --> 00:33:23,340
I won't need it.
